  • Packages that use IChatroomMsg 
    Package Description
    chatapp.messages.chat  
    chatapp.utils  
    common.FinalProjectAPI.chatroom
    Contains interfaces for interacting with Chatrooms, including IChatroom (the actual chatroom object itself) and IMsgReceiver (the adapter that allows a user to communicate with a remote Chatroom object).
    common.FinalProjectAPI.message.chatroom
    Contains all message types that can be received and processed by an IMsgReceiver inside a Chatroom.
